{"tid":466734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半夜三更上樓購物　男子報稱遇劫失千元","createTime":"2017-11-12T23:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T03:03:27.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8d64552a64ba6693cebb6f2c4723cea913099523","tid":466734,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/132966/thumbnail/9c8ca1adeb5925b729c29c5f69807b98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F132966%2Fthumbnail%2F9c8ca1adeb5925b729c29c5f69807b98.jpg&h=fd025ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/975174/xlarge/94721911507978e7edaa17be5d252669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F975174%2Fxlarge%2F94721911507978e7edaa17be5d252669.jpg&h=592ec00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到旺角劫案現場調查。(陳永武攝)<br />\n<br />\n凌晨零時許，一名中年男子途經旺角亞皆老街56號對開，報警稱遇劫。警員到場調查，據悉有人報稱事發時到附近的樓上單位「購物」，途至上址時卻遭人打劫，搶走大約1,000元現金。警員在附近兜截賊人無果，用警車將事主載返警署作進一步調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/975173/xlarge/e849c3ad905e661a092d118979c73692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F975173%2Fxlarge%2Fe849c3ad905e661a092d118979c73692.jpg&h=4ecdc066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員向男事主了解事件。(陳永武攝)<br />\n<br />\n另外，凌晨2時半左右，一名59歲姓孫男子報案指，途經上水寶運路95號對開時，突遭賊人從後用石頭襲擊，繼而另一賊人遭搶走金鍊。救護員趕至為傷者檢查，發現他頭、胸口及手受傷，即場急救後送到北區醫院進一步治療。據悉被搶走的金鍊約值5.3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，案件列作「行劫」，交由大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。警方正追緝2名年約20歲至30歲中國籍男子，身高約1.7米，中等身材，短黑髮，案發時分別身穿黑色及灰色上衣，其中一人戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132966/%E5%8D%8A%E5%A4%9C%E4%B8%89%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%A8%93%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB%E5%A4%B1%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F132966%2F%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25A4%259C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%258A%25AB%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=944652d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132966/%E5%8D%8A%E5%A4%9C%E4%B8%89%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%A8%93%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB%E5%A4%B1%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"0fffde3f61942b44db5c211b6befae8cbba93d46","tid":466734,"uid":28151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a968bea168f87bc4e95a01546cd60cf3d59e4c","tid":466734,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:11:35.000Z","msg":"買春都係買野黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba176b562b5f99c247026e9b58c9d88a37714d1","tid":466734,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:12:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c975221ddbc626fcaa830d26571927daf9e0c7cf","tid":466734,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上水寶運路有得叫雞？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外</span><br />\n<br />\n咁都睇唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2540e0eb649